sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Harness TS<br/>(Agent Loop)
    participant HC as HermesClient TS<br/>(gRPC Client)
    participant HS as HermesServer PY<br/>(gRPC Server)
    participant LLM as LLM API<br/>(OpenAI/Anthropic)

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Stream Chat (推荐模式) ═══════

    H->>+HC: streamChat(request)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC StreamChat(ChatRequest)
    Note over HS: 消息格式转换<br/>Harness → Hermes 格式
    HS->>+LLM: stream ChatCompletion
    LLM-->>-HS: stream token chunks

    loop 每收到一个 token
        HS-->>HC: ChatChunk{content_delta, index}
        HC-->>H: yield chunk
        H->>H: onText() → ws.send(text:delta)
    end

    alt 有工具调用
        HS-->>HC: ChatChunk{tool_call_delta, id, name, args}
        HC-->>H: yield tool_call chunk
        H->>H: 收集 tool_call 信息
    end

    HS-->>HC: ChatChunk{finish_reason, usage}
    HC-->>H: yield final chunk
    alt finish_reason == TOOL_CALLS
        H->>H: 解析 tool_calls<br/>执行工具循环
        H->>H: 将工具结果加入 messages
        H->>+HC: streamChat(next_request)
        HC->>+HS: gRPC StreamChat(next_request)
        Note over HS: 继续下一轮迭代
    else finish_reason == STOP
        Note over H: 返回最终文本结果
    end
    deactivate HC
    deactivate HS

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Non-streaming Chat ═══════

    H->>+HC: chat(request)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC Chat(ChatRequest)
    HS->>+LLM: ChatCompletion (non-streaming)
    LLM-->>-HS: full response
    HS-->>-HC: ChatResponse{content, tool_calls, usage}
    HC-->>-H: return ChatResponse
    H->>H: 解析响应, 执行工具

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Memory Save ═══════

    H->>+HC: memorySave(request)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC HermesMemory.Save(SaveRequest)
    HS->>HS: 生成嵌入向量 (调用嵌入模型)
    HS->>HS: 存储到 Memory Provider<br/>(Holographic/Honcho 等)
    HS-->>-HC: SaveResponse{memory_id, deduplicated}
    HC-->>-H: return memory_id

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Memory Search ═══════

    H->>+HC: memorySearch(query)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC HermesMemory.Search(SearchRequest)
    HS->>HS: 生成查询嵌入向量
    HS->>HS: 向量相似度搜索
    HS-->>-HC: SearchResponse{results[], total_count, time_ms}
    HC-->>-H: return MemoryItem[]

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Skill Execution ═══════

    H->>+HC: skillExecute(skillId, task, params)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC HermesSkills.ExecuteSkill(ExecuteSkillRequest)
    HS->>HS: 加载 SKILL.md 内容
    HS->>HS: 填充模板变量 ${...}
    HS->>HS: 调用 LLM 执行技能任务
    HS-->>-HC: ExecuteSkillResponse{result, success, usage, time_ms}
    HC-->>-H: return result

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Agent Task (完整代理执行) ═══════

    H->>+HC: agentRunTask(task, config)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC HermesAgent.RunTask(TaskRequest)
    HS->>HS: 启动 AIAgent 实例
    HS->>HS: 初始化 Memory Manager
    HS->>HS: 加载 Skills

    loop Agent Loop 迭代
        HS->>HS: assemblePrompt()
        HS->>+LLM: stream ChatCompletion
        LLM-->>-HS: response
        HS->>HS: 解析响应
        opt has tool_calls
            HS->>HS: execute tool
            HS->>HS: save to memory
        end
    end

    HS-->>-HC: TaskResponse{result, iterations, usage, steps}
    HC-->>-H: return final result

    Note over H,LLM: ═══════ Error Handling ═══════

    H->>+HC: chat(request)
    HC->>+HS: gRPC Chat(request)
    alt LLM API 临时错误 (503)
        HS-->>HC: gRPC status UNAVAILABLE
        Note over HC: 指数退避重试<br/>100ms → 200ms → 400ms
        HC->>+HS: gRPC Chat(request) (重试)
        HS->>+LLM: ChatCompletion
        LLM-->>-HS: response
        HS-->>-HC: ChatResponse
        HC-->>-H: return response
    else Rate Limit (429)
        HS-->>HC: gRPC status RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED<br/>retry_after_ms: 5000
        Note over HC: 等待 5 秒后重试
        HC->>+HS: gRPC Chat(request) (等待后重试)
    else 熔断器打开
        Note over HC: Circuit Breaker OPEN<br/>快速失败, 不调用 gRPC
        HC-->>-H: throw CircuitBreakerError
        Note over H: 回退到直接 LLM Provider 调用
    end
